M|references|| Cohort retention curves | Weekly | Newer cohorts retain better |
M|references|| Feature adoption rates | Weekly | Core features used by 60%+ of actives |
M|references|| Customer health score | Weekly | 80%+ of customers in "healthy" range |
M|references|| Net customer growth | Monthly | Positive and accelerating |
M|references|| Metric | Frequency | Target |
M|references||--------|-----------|--------|
M|references|| Viral coefficient (K) | Weekly | Approaching or exceeding 1.0 |
M|references|| Viral cycle time | Weekly | Decreasing |
M|references|| Share/invite rate | Daily | Stable or increasing |
M|references|| Invited user conversion | Weekly | Increasing |
M|references|| Organic traffic percentage | Monthly | Increasing |
M|references|| Metric | Frequency | Target |
M|references||--------|-----------|--------|
M|references|| CAC by channel | Weekly | Stable or decreasing |
M|references|| LTV/CAC ratio | Monthly | 3:1 or better |
M|references|| Payback period | Monthly | Under 12 months |
